  "lernziele": "<p>Students will be able to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>explain the purpose and the typical use cases for modern cryptographic primitives,</li>\n<li>identify common issues when applying or implementing cryptographic primitives. For example, the use of weak randomness&nbsp;generators, or padding oracle attacks</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>recognize the importance of cryptographic agility at the example of post-quantum cryptography</li>\n</ul>",
